  "detailed_description": "Have you ever wondered what those Christmas glass balls are really hiding?<br />\r\nBut I know..! And this Christmas story is not as usual. Yes, there is the Santa Claus, his reindeer and gifts for children. But these are not at all the gifts that a child expects for Christmas. And you can’t even imagine what awaits you that night!<br />\r\nHave you ever pissed on snowmen and elves? Or fed poisoned popcorn to the deer? I'm sure not! And it’s unlikely that you went down into a cursed dungeon with ghosts to find gifts and the treasured key to the chest!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWaiting for you:<br />\r\n- Search and sort items<br />\r\n- Explore the dungeon<br />\r\n- Interact with Christmas creatures<br />\r\n- Launch Santa to the moon<br />\r\n- And lots of funny moments",
  "about_the_game": "Have you ever wondered what those Christmas glass balls are really hiding?<br />\r\nBut I know..! And this Christmas story is not as usual. Yes, there is the Santa Claus, his reindeer and gifts for children. But these are not at all the gifts that a child expects for Christmas. And you can’t even imagine what awaits you that night!<br />\r\nHave you ever pissed on snowmen and elves? Or fed poisoned popcorn to the deer? I'm sure not! And it’s unlikely that you went down into a cursed dungeon with ghosts to find gifts and the treasured key to the chest!<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWaiting for you:<br />\r\n- Search and sort items<br />\r\n- Explore the dungeon<br />\r\n- Interact with Christmas creatures<br />\r\n- Launch Santa to the moon<br />\r\n- And lots of funny moments",
